name: Blue Galaxy
description: Procedural system made with trapcode particular [05-02-18] following a workflow recipe I was planning to record a tutorial on. Upon realizing the amount of already existing tutorials on the subject I never did record it. Instead I ended up creating a visual pack for Envato release 	[06-06-18]. Images in the background are pictures from the hubble telescope If you need this in 2K for commercial purposes you can find the link in the description of this youtube demo [ https://bit.ly/3tTL7lF ] //////////////////////////////// SPECS : 1:1 | 800x800 | 180 | 24FPS
